---
title: Creamy Mushroom Soup with Thyme plus Garlic Bread
description: Rich, creamy mushroom soup is a comforting dish that spotlights the earthy, umami flavors of mushrooms in a velvety base. You'll sauté mushrooms with thyme and garlic, then simmer it all to perfection and swirl with tangy crème fraîche. Sprinkle with fresh scallion greens and serve with toasty, savory garlic bread for a match made in soup heaven.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/675744d5daedc2bd12958283-7a35f239.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/675744d5daedc2bd12958283-en-US.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/creamy-mushroom-soup-with-thyme-675744d5daedc2bd12958283
course: main course
author: Michelle Doll Olson
cuisine: North America
time required: 25 minutes
servings: 2
nutrition:
  calories: 630 kcal
